column5: I put together a fishing video from my last outing from shore. Thought you guys might like to see it. I filmed it by myself so it was difficult to get everything in there! I won't even get into trying to edit it on my slow computer, lol. Hope you enjoy. The next one will be better, I promise!
DUDE!  Great video and who is that you used for the music?  i can't stop humming that after a few views.  GREAT JOB!
Hery cool - nice stretch of water and scenery there
real good video
Very nice!
Awesome vid!  What were you using for a camera(s)?
Really nice job....  appreciate all the time it took to put that together.
Excellent production values, you should be doing a lot more of these!   At the bottom right it says Foo Fighters, Stranger Things Have Happened.
Very good,   should I ask, is that what you do for a living? That stuff should be on TV  . Make a good commercial for product.
Hey great video and the music was a awesome choice to. That sure is a nice area your fishing in.
Thanks for sharing

Diltsy, That is a great video and I checked out a few others too. Life in Plastic http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qAlY5bLc4A4&feature=related is very well done. Great vid. You should all check it out. Ryan has mad skills.
Diltsy, hope to see more!
you must have a great camera!  that's some crisp footy!
Excellent stuff!!  Hate to say it, but, I agree with Geoff  that tune is awesome!
Very nice footage - and Pearl Jam, Foo Fighters... great taste in music.
Nice compilation, thanks for sharing!
nice work!
That's a sweet video. Really like the multiple angles and nice touch with the slow-mo at the end when you hold up the bass. Really well done it has a great feel to it.
That's fantastic stuff!  Thanks for sharing...looking forward to more
great tune ,,,,, it reminds of so much about what I think about when solo fishing...  gonna share it on my FB page
Terrific video! You did some great editing, had some great camera angles, and of course we always like looking at fish too!
